snippet.title: I made a Haunted House Cleaning Simulator
snippet.description:
It's time for another game devlog.
Watch me struggle as I make a game a learn a new game engine: The Unreal Engine.
Yes, I learned how to make a game in Unreal Engine, a  Haunted House Cleaning Simulator and it was a hell of a ride.

►►DOWNLOAD THE GAME►►
Itchio►https://lixiangames.itch.io/late-night-mop
GameJolt►https://gamejolt.com/games/LateNightMop/751824

►►TUTORIALS I MENTIONED AND FISCHER►►
Follow Fischer►https://www.twitch.tv/f_fischer
Pontypants►https://youtu.be/nY4Q8cYBLP8
Codekitten►https://youtu.be/gmYvSPj8rmI


►►MY STUFF►►

Merch► teespring.com/stores/lixian


I really hope you guys enjoy it
Love you all
